{"tid":230220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"18歲少女墮電騙    找換店醒目東主揭破","createTime":"2017-05-05T07:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T13:20:07.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42093aa9a1f8a080c9b2c4d98ba4a4ea0c5456aa","tid":230220,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:50:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170505/large/1493968574_871f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170505%2Flarge%2F1493968574_871f.jpg&h=bbd418b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名18歲少女，較早前收到自稱入境處人員的電話，指她涉及刑事罪行，電話輾轉駁到內地執法人員，對方要求她滙款2萬港元到內地一個指定戶口。少女不虞有詐，下午1時許拿著鈔票到北角堡壘街一間找換店滙款。45歲姓曾東主察覺可疑，查問下得知始末，懷疑少女受騙，代為報警。事件中少女沒有損失。<br />\n<br />\n東主事後稱，少女到來滙款時神色慌張，一時指家人犯事，一時又說自己犯事，不知所措。當時她拿着手機，歹徒就在手機另一方。東主於是伸手出櫥窗關掉她的通話，並安慰她要冷靜下來，再告訴她應該是騙案。"},{"pid":"f55389d8705c3e8a14cec8d40709565dc9348c6f","tid":230220,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:40:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38009d60a15b4dad1f94363de64353b52d6a3baf","tid":230220,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:42:06.000Z","msg":"18歲有2萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有錢"},{"pid":"fa301172346217f831dce30336ea17f9e4c7640e","tid":230220,"uid":54183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:43:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"373d63273137196b995b0fef3cc4de0ff8405783","tid":230220,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:45:10.000Z","msg":"智障"},{"pid":"2013f7f10ad61a393be02183cf6d8bcd21912b67","tid":230220,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:43:37.000Z","msg":"新移民？"},{"pid":"7f181aece6b37f5c0b3ed81c4d378bdb5f0958e9","tid":230220,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:47:42.000Z","msg":"阻人搵食找